sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    title SEQ-2B: Create Calendar — Full HITL Flow (missing info, conflict, edit, cancel)

    actor User
    participant MC as Message Channel
    participant BE as Backend API
    participant Agent as Agent Orchestrator
    participant LLM as LLM Provider
    participant TR as Tool Router
    participant Cal as Calendar Tool
    participant GCal as Google Calendar API
    participant ST as Storage / Memory

    User->>MC: "Tạo lịch họp review chiều mai mời anh Minh"
    MC->>BE: Forward message
    BE-)ST: Async log raw message
    BE->>Agent: Forward request

    Agent->>ST: Load context + contact graph + history
    ST-->>Agent: Context + contacts (anh Minh=minh@)

    Agent->>LLM: Understand request + extract params
    LLM-->>Agent: intent=calendar.create, date=tomorrow,<br/>attendees=[minh@], title=Review,<br/>missing=[time, duration, location]

    Note over Agent: WRITE action → HIGH risk → HITL required

    %% === EDGE CASE 1: Thiếu thông tin ===
    rect rgb(255, 249, 230)
        Note over Agent,User: MISSING INFO — hỏi lại user
        Agent-->>BE: Hỏi lại params còn thiếu
        BE-->>MC: Reply
        MC-->>User: "Mấy giờ? Họp bao lâu?<br/>Phòng nào hoặc online?"
        User->>MC: "3h chiều, 1 tiếng, Meet"
        MC->>BE: Forward
        BE->>Agent: Bổ sung: time=15:00,<br/>duration=60min, location=Meet

        Agent->>LLM: Re-extract với params đầy đủ
        LLM-->>Agent: All params OK
    end

    %% === EDGE CASE 2: Xung đột lịch ===
    Agent->>TR: list_events(tomorrow, 15:00-16:00, attendees)
    TR->>Cal: list_events(...)
    Cal->>GCal: events.list(...)
    GCal-->>Cal: 1 event: "Standup 15:00-15:30"
    Cal-->>TR: Conflict found
    TR-->>Agent: Conflict: anh Minh bận 15:00-15:30

    rect rgb(255, 243, 224)
        Note over Agent,User: CONFLICT — đề xuất slot thay thế
        Agent->>LLM: Tìm slot thay thế gần nhất
        LLM-->>Agent: Suggest 16:00-17:00
        Agent-->>BE: Báo conflict + đề xuất
        BE-->>MC: Reply
        MC-->>User: "⚠️ 15h anh Minh có Standup.<br/>Đổi 16h-17h được không?"
        User->>MC: "OK 16h"
        MC->>BE: Forward
        BE->>Agent: Confirm time=16:00-17:00

        Agent->>TR: list_events(tomorrow, 16:00-17:00, attendees)
        TR->>Cal: list_events(...)
        Cal->>GCal: events.list(...)
        GCal-->>Cal: No events
        Cal-->>TR: No conflicts
        TR-->>Agent: Slot trống OK
    end

    %% === HITL GATE ===
    rect rgb(252, 228, 236)
        Note over Agent: HITL GATE
        Agent-)ST: Lưu pending_action
        Agent-->>BE: Approval request + preview
        BE-->>MC: Preview
        MC-->>User: "📅 Review 16h-17h mai<br/>👥 anh Minh · 📎 Meet<br/><br/>✅ Tạo | ✏️ Sửa | ❌ Hủy"

        %% === EDGE CASE 3: User sửa ===
        alt ✏️ Sửa
            User->>MC: "Thêm chị Lan và anh Tuấn"
            MC->>BE: edit + instruction
            BE->>Agent: HITL edit

            Agent->>ST: Resolve contacts từ contact graph
            ST-->>Agent: chị Lan=lan@, anh Tuấn=tuan@

            Agent-)ST: Log edit request
            Agent-->>BE: Updated preview
            BE-->>MC: Preview mới
            MC-->>User: "📅 Review 16h-17h mai<br/>👥 anh Minh, chị Lan, anh Tuấn<br/>📎 Meet<br/><br/>✅ Tạo | ✏️ Sửa | ❌ Hủy"

            User->>MC: ✅ Tạo
            MC->>BE: approved
            BE->>Agent: HITL approved

        %% === EDGE CASE 4: User hủy ===
        else ❌ Hủy
            User->>MC: ❌ Hủy
            MC->>BE: rejected
            BE->>Agent: HITL rejected

            Agent-)ST: Log rejection + reason
            Agent->>LLM: Summarize cancellation
            LLM-->>Agent: Cancel message
            Agent-->>BE: Response
            BE-->>MC: Reply
            MC-->>User: "Đã hủy. Cần tạo lịch khác không?"
            Note over Agent: Kết thúc — không execute
        end
    end

    %% === Execute (chỉ khi approved) ===
    Agent->>TR: create_event(title, time, attendees, meet)
    TR->>Cal: create_event(...)
    Cal->>GCal: events.insert(...)
    GCal-->>Cal: event_id + meet_link
    Cal-->>TR: Created event
    TR-->>Agent: OK

    Agent-)ST: Async log tool_calls + HITL decision (redacted)

    Agent->>LLM: Summarize kết quả
    LLM-->>Agent: Confirmation

    Agent-)ST: Update session memory / audit metadata
    Agent-->>BE: Final response
    BE-->>MC: Reply
    MC-->>User: "✅ Đã tạo Review 16h-17h mai<br/>📎 meet.google.com/abc-xyz<br/>👥 anh Minh, chị Lan, anh Tuấn"
